var chapter = 'Thou hast made me endless, such is thy pleasure. This frail vessel thou emptiest again and again, and fillest it ever with fresh life. \n' + 'This little flute of a reed thou hast carried over hills and dales, and hast breathed through it melodies eternally new. \n' + 'At the immortal touch of thy hands my little heart loses its limits in joy and gives birth to utterance ineffable.';
export default chapter;
